 British people]]\n[[Category:19th-century British monarchs]]\n[[Category:18th-century Royal Navy personnel]]\n[[Category:19th-century Royal Navy personnel]]\n[[Category:Royal Navy personnel of the American Revolutionary War]]\n[[Category:Burials at St George's Chapel, Windsor Castle]]\n[[Category:Dukes of Clarence]]\n[[Category:Peers of Great Britain created by George III]]\n[[Category:Earls of Munster]]\n[[Category:Peers of Ireland created by George III]]\n[[Category:Fellows of the Society of Antiquaries of London]]\n[[Category:Great Masters of the Order of the Bath]]\n[[Category:Hanoverian princes]]\n[[Category:Kings of Hanover]]\n[[Category:Knights of the Garter]]\n[[Category:Knights of the Thistle]]\n[[Category:Lord High Admirals]]\n[[Category:Members of the Privy Council of Great Britain]]\n[[Category:Monarchs of the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:People from Westminster]]\n[[Category:Princes of Great Britain]]\n[[Category:Princes of the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:Knights of the Golden Fleece of Spain]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of St. Andrew]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of St. Alexander Nevsky]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of the Black Eagle]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the House Order of Fidelity]]\n[[Category:Knights Grand Cross of the Order of the Z\u00e4hringer Lion]]\n[[Category:Knights Grand Cross of the Order of the Crown (W\u00fcrttemberg)]]\n[[Category:Royal Navy personnel of the Napoleonic Wars]]\n[[Category:Supernumerary Knights of the Order of the Holy Spirit]]\n[[Category:Freemasons of the United Grand Lodge of England]]\n[[Category:Monarchs of the Isle of Man]]\n", "name_user": "DrKay", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_IV_of_the_United_Kingdom"}
