orf\n| Crainim\u0103t\n|- \n| Ballendorf\n| Balomiru de C\u00e2mp\n|- \n| B\u00e4rendorf\n| Beriu\n|- \n| Bartholom\u00e4\n| Bartolomeu, [[Bra\u015fov County]]\n|- \n| Batiz\n| Batiz\n|- \n| Baumgarten/Bistriz\n| Bungard\n|- \n| Baumgarten/Hermannstadt\n| Bungard, [[Sibiu County]]\n|- \n| Bekokten\n| B\u0103rcu\u0163\n|- \n| Bell\n| Buia, [[Sibiu County]]\n|- \n| Belleschdorf\n| Idiciu\n|- \n| Benden\n| Biia\n|- \n| Benzenz\n| Bin\u0163in\u0163i, nowadays Aurel Vlaicu\n|- \n| Bernhardsdorf\n| Bernadea\n|- \n| Besotten\n| Buza\n|- \n| Bethlen/Bistriz\n| Beclean\n|- \n| Bidda\n| Bidiu\n|- \n| Bierldorf\n| B\u00e2rla\n|- \n| Billak\n| Domne\u015fti\n|- \n| Birk\n| Petelea, [[Mure\u015f County]]\n|- \n| Birnbaum\n| Ghirbom\n|- \n| Birth\u00e4lm (+ Fettendorf)\n| [[Biertan]], [[Sibiu County]]\n|- \n| Bistritz (+ Niederwallendorf)\n| [[Bistri\u0163a]], [[Bistri\u0163a-N\u0103s\u0103ud County]]\n|- \n| Bladenmarkt\n| B\u0103l\u0103u\u015feri\n|- \n| Blasendorf\n| [[Blaj]]\n|- \n| Blumendorf\n| [[Belin, Covasna|Belin]]\n|- \n| Blutroth (+ Paulsdorf)\n| Berghin\n|- \n| Bodeln\n| Budila\n|- \n| Bodendorf\n| Bune\u015fti\n|- \n| Bodesdorf\n| [[Budu\u015f]], [[Bistri\u0163a-N\u0103s\u0103ud County]]\n|- \n| Bogeschdorf\n| [[B\u0103gaciu]], [[Mure\u015f County]]\n|- \n| Bonnesdorf\n| Boian\n|- \n| Borbant\n| [[B\u0103r\u0103ban\u0163]], [[Alba County]]\n|- \n| Botsch\n| [[Bato\u015f]], [[Mure\u015f County]]\n|- \n| Botschard\n| [[Bucerdea Gr\u00e2noas\u0103]], [[Alba County]]\n|- \n| Braller\n| Bruiu\n|- \n| Breit\n| Bretea\n|- \n| Brenndorf\n| [[Bod, Bra\u015fov|Bod]], [[Bra\u015fov County]]\n|- \n| Broos\n| [[Or\u0103\u015ftie]], [[Hunedoara County]]\n|- \n| Bruck\n| [[Bon\u0163ida]], [[Cluj County]]\n|- \n| Buchholz (+ Schalgo)\n| Bohol\u0163 \n|- \n| Budenbach\n| Sibiel\n|- \n| Bulkesch\n| B\u0103lcaciu\n|- \n| Burg Zebernek\n| Cetatea de la Vurp\u0103r\n|- \n| Burgberg bei Hermannstadt\n| [[Vurp\u0103r, Sibiu|Vurp\u0103r]], [[Sibiu County]]\n|- \n| Burgberg bei M\u00fchlbach\n| [[Vurp\u0103r, Alba|Vurp\u0103r]], [[Alba County]]\n|- \n| B\u00fcrgesch\n| B\u00e2rghi\u015f\n|- \n| Burghalle\n| Orheiul Bistri\u0163ei\n|- \n| Burglos\n| [[Dej]]\n|- \n| Bu\u00dfd bei Mediasch\n| Buzd\n|- \n| [[Bu\u00dfd]] bei M\u00fchlbach\n| [[Bu\u00dfd|Boz]]\n|- \n| Garndorf\n| Ardan, [[Bistri\u0163a-N\u0103s\u0103ud County]]\n|- \n| Dahl\n| D\u0103i\u015foara, [[Bra\u015fov County]]\n|- \n| Dallen bei M\u00fchlbach\n| Deal, [[Alba County]]\n|- \n| Dallendorf\n| [[Daia Rom\u00e2n\u0103]], [[Alba County]]\n|- \n| Dengel\n| [[Daia, Mure\u015f|Daia]] (used to be Daia S\u0103seasc\u0103, Commune of  Apold), [[Mure\u015f County]]\n|- \n| Denndorf\n| [[Daia, Mure\u015f|Daia]] (Commune of  [[Bahnea]]), [[Mure\u015f County]]\n|- \n| Dersch\n| [[D\u00e2rju]]\n|- \n| Deutschbach\n| [[Valea Sasului, Alba|Valea Sasului]]\n|- \n| Deutschbudak\n| [[Budacu de Jos]]\n|- \n| Deutschendorf\n| [[Mintiu Gherlii]]\n|- \n| Deutschkreuz\n| [[Cri\u0163]]\n|- \n| Deutschpien\n| [[Pianul de Jos]]\n|- \n| Deutschtekes\n| [[Ticu\u015ful Vechi]]\n|- \n| Deutschwei\u00dfkirch\n| [[Viscri]], [[Bra\u015fov County]]\n|- \n| Deutschzepling\n| [[Dedrad]]\n|- \n| Diemrich\n| [[Deva, Romania|Deva]], [[Hunedoara County]]\n|- \n| Dienesdorf\n| [[\u015eieu Odorhei]], [[Bistri\u0163a-N\u0103s\u0103ud County]]\n|- \n| Dobring\n| [[Dob\u00eerca]]\n|- \n| Donnersmarkt\n| [[M\u0103n\u0103rade]]\n|- \n| Dopich\n| [[Dopca]]\n|- \n| Draas\n| [[Dr\u0103u\u015feni]]\n|- \n| Dreikirchen\n| [[Teiu\u015f]], [[Alba County]]\n|- \n| Dunesdorf\n| [[Dane\u015f]], [[Mure\u015f County]]\n|- \n| Durles\n| [[D\u00e2rlos]], [[Sibiu County]]\n|- \n| D\u00fcrrbach\n| [[Dip\u015fa]]\n|- \n| Ehrgang\n| [[Ernea]]\n|- \n| Eibesdorf\n| [[Ighi\u015ful Nou]]\n|- \n| Eisch\n| [[F\u00e2nt\u00e2nele, Bistri\u0163a-N\u0103s\u0103ud|F\u00e2nt\u00e2nele]]\n|- \n| Eisdorf\n| [[lone\u015fti]]\n|- \n| Eisenburg\n| [[Rimetea]]\n|- \n| Elisabethstadt\n| [[Dumbr\u0103veni]]\n|- \n| Elsterdorf\n| [[Sereca]]\n|- \n| Emerichsdorf\n| [[S\u0