\u015fti, Alba|R\u0103de\u015fti]]\n|- \n| Neudorf/Hermannstadt\n| [[Noul]]\n|- \n| Neudorf/Kronstadt (+ Hopfenseifen)\n| [[Satu Nou, Bra\u015fov|Satu Nou]]\n|- \n| Neudorf/Sch\u00e4\u00dfburg\n| [[Noul S\u0103sesc]]\n|- \n| Neudorf/Wb.\n| [[Ohaba]]\n|- \n| Neuflagen\n| [[Mureni]]\n|- \n| Neumarkt\n| [[T\u00e2rgu-Mure\u015f]]\n|- \n| Neuschlo\u00df\n| [[Gherla]]\n|- \n| Neustadt/Agnetheln\n| [[Noi\u015ftat]]\n|- \n| Neustadt/Kronstadt\n| [[Cristian, Bra\u015fov|Cristian]]\n|- \n| Niedereidisch\n| [[Ideciu de Jos]]\n|- \n| Niederneudorf\n| [[Corvine\u015fti]]\n|- \n| Nieresch\n| [[Nire\u015f]]\n|- \n| Nimesch\n| [[Nem\u015fa]]\n|- \n| Nindorf\n| [[Nimigea de jos]]\n|- \n| Nu\u00dfbach\n| [[M\u0103ieru\u015f]]\n|- \n| Nussendorf\n| [[N\u0103s\u0103ud]]\n|- \n| Oberblasendorf\n| [[Bl\u0103jenii de Sus]]\n|- \n| Oberbrodsdorf\n| [[Vinerea]]\n|- \n| Obereidisch\n| [[Ideciu de Sus]]\n|- \n| Oberkreuz\n| [[Cristur-\u015eieu]]\n|- \n| Oberneudorf\n| [[Cetate, Bistri\u0163a-N\u0103s\u0103ud|Cetate]]\n|- \n| Oberr\u00f6bendorf\n| [[V\u0103tava]]\n|- \n| Oberschebesch\n| [[Sebi\u015f]]\n|- \n| Ochsendorf (+ Lauterburg)\n| [[Boi\u0163a]]\n|- \n| Odendorf\n| [[Apalina]]\n|- \n| Offenburg\n| [[Baia de Arie\u015f]]\n|- \n| Okne\n| [[Ocni\u0163a]]\n|- \n| Panagen\n| [[S\u00e2ncel|P\u0103nade]]\n|- \n| Pa\u00dfbusch\n| [[Posmu\u015f]]\n|- \n| Perka\u00df\n| [[Pricaz]]\n|- \n| Pernseifen\n| [[B\u0103i\u0163a, Hunedoara|B\u0103i\u0163a]]\n|- \n| Peschendorf\n| [[Stej\u0103reni]]\n|- \n| Petersberg\n| [[S\u00eenpetru]]\n|- \n| Petersdorf/Bistriz\n| [[Petri\u015f]]\n|- \n| Petersdorf/Mediasch\n| [[Peti\u015f]]\n|- \n| Petersdorf/M\u00fchlbach\n| [[Petre\u015fti, Alba|Petre\u015fti]]\n|- \n| Petsch\n| [[Petecu]]\n|- \n| Pintak/Bistriz\n| [[Sl\u0103tini\u0163a]]\n|- \n| Pintak/Td.\n| [[Pinticu]]\n|- \n| Pojana\n| [[Poiana Sibiului]]\n|- \n| Pr\u00e4nzdorf\n| [[Suseni, Mure\u015f|Suseni]]\n|- \n| Pretai\n| [[Bratei]]\n|- \n| Probstdorf/Agnetheln\n| [[Stej\u0103ri\u015fu]]\n|- \n| Pr\u00fcden\n| [[Prod, Romania]]\n|- \n| Puschendorf\n| [[P\u0103ucea]]\n|- \n| Radeln\n| [[Roade\u015f]]\n|- \n| Ragelsdorf\n| [[Ragla]]\n|- \n| Rakowitza\n| [[Racovi\u0163a (disambiguation)|Racovi\u0163a]]\n|- \n| Ratsch\n| [[Reciu]]\n|- \n| Rauthal\n| [[Roandola]]\n|- \n| Reckentek\n| [[Reteag]]\n|- \n| Reichau\n| [[R\u0103h\u0103u]]\n|- \n| Reichesdorf\n| [[Richi\u015f]]\n|- \n| Reissen\n| [[Rusu B\u00e2rg\u0103ului]]\n|- \n| Rekitta\n| [[R\u0103chita, Alba|R\u0103chita]]\n|- \n| Rependorf\n| [[R\u00e2pa (disambiguation)|R\u00e2pa]]\n|- \n| Reps\n| [[Rupea]]\n|- \n| Retersdorf\n| [[Reti\u015f]]\n|- \n| Reu\u00dfdorf\n| [[Bahnea|Cund]]\n|- \n| Reu\u00dfd\u00f6rfchen\n| [[Ruscior (disambiguation)|Ruscior]]\n|- \n| Reu\u00dfen/Bistriz\n| [[S\u0103r\u0103\u0163el, Bistri\u0163a-N\u0103s\u0103ud|S\u0103r\u0103\u0163el]]\n|- \n| Reu\u00dfen/Mediasch\n| [[Ru\u015fi, Sibiu|Ru\u015fi]]\n|- \n| Reu\u00dfmarkt (+Mondorf, + Wei\u00dfkirch, + Sankt-Georgen)\n| [[Miercurea Sibiului]]\n|- \n| Ringelkirch\n| [[Valea Ringhili]]\n|- \n| Rod\n| Rod\n|- \n| Rode\n| [[Zag\u0103r]]\n|- \n| Rodna\n| [[Rodna]]\n|- \n| Rohrbach\n| [[Rodbav]]\n|- \n| Rosch\n| [[R\u0103v\u0103\u015fel]]\n|- \n| Roseln\n| [[Ruja]]\n|- \n| Rosenau\n| [[R\u00e2\u015fnov]]\n|- \n| Roter Turm\n| [[Turnul Ro\u015fu]]\n|- \n| Rothbach\n| [[Rotbav]]\n|- \n| Rothberg/Hermannstadt\n| [[Ro\u015fia, Sibiu|Ro\u015fia]]\n|- \n| Rothkirch/Bistriz\n| [[Strugureni]]\n|- \n| Rothkirch/M\u00fchlbach\n| [[Ro\u015fia de Seca\u015f]]\n|- \n| Ruckersdorf\n| [[Ruc\u0103r]]\n|- \n| Rum\u00e4nisch Baierdorf\n| [[Mintiu (disambiguation)|Mintiu]]\n|- \n| Rum\u00e4nisch Budak\n| [[Budacul de Sus]]\n|- \n| Rum\u00e4nisch Eibesdorf\n| [[Ighi\u015ful Vechi]]\n|- \n| Rum\u00e4nisch Lasseln\n| [[Lasl\u0103ul Mare]]\n|- \n| Rum\u00e4nisch Neudorf\n| [[Noul Rom\u00e2n]]\n|- \n| Rum\u00e4nisch Pien\n| [[Pianul de Sus]]\n|- \n| Rum\u00e4nisch Sankt Georgen\n| [[S\u00e2ngeorz-B\u0103i]]\n|- \n| Rum\u00e4nisch Tekes\n| [[Ticu\u015ful Nou]]\n|- \n| Rumes