f\n| [[Cun\u0163a]]\n|- \n| Zendersch\n| [[Senereu\u015f]]\n|- \n| Zernest\n| [[Z\u0103rne\u015fti]]\n|- \n| Zied\n| [[Veseud, Chirp\u0103r, Sibiu|Veseud]]\n|- \n| Ziegenstein\n| [[Piatra Craivii]]\n|- \n| Ziegenthal\n| [[\u0162ichindeal]]\n|- \n| Zoltendorf\n| [[Mihai Viteazu]]\n|- \n| Zood\n| [[Sadu]]\n|- \n| Zuckmantel\n| [[\u0162igmandru]], [[Mure\u015f County]]\n|}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Transylvanian Saxon localities}}\n[[Category:Transylvanian Saxon communities|*]]\n[[Category:Transylvanian-Saxon people|Localities]]\n[[Category:Transylvania in the Kingdom of Hungary|Saxon localities]]\n[[Category:Alternative names of European places]]\n[[Category:Lists of place names]]\n[[Category:Names of places in Romania|Transylvania]]\n", "name_user": "Rosenborg BK Fan", "label": "safe", "comment": "Updated introduction", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Transylvanian_Saxon_localities"}
