ion series endings]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|South Korean television series}}\n{{about||the original TV series of the same title|Mother (Japanese TV series)}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name            = Mother\n| image                = Mother (South Korean TV series).jpg\n| caption              = Promotional poster\n| show_name_2          = Call Me Mother<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dramafever.com/drama/5150/Call_Me_Mother/|title=Call Me Mother|website=[[DramaFever]]|publisher=DramaFever Corp.|accessdate=January 25, 2018}}</ref>\n| native_name          = {{Infobox name module|hangul=\ub9c8\ub354}}\n| genre                = {{ubl|[[Drama]]|[[Thriller (genre)#Suspense|Suspense]]}}\n| developer            = [[Studio Dragon]]\n| writer               = Chung Seo-kyung\n| director             = Kim Cheol-kyu\n| creative_director    = \n| starring             = {{ubl|[[Lee Bo-young]]|[[Heo Yool]]|[[Lee Hye-young (actress, born 1962)|Lee Hye-young]]}}\n| theme_music_composer = \n| opentheme            = \n| endtheme             = \n| composer             = \n| country              = South Korea\n| language             = Korean\n| num_episodes         = 16\n| executive_producer   = {{ubl|Kim Jin-yi|Park Ji-young}}\n| producer             = \n| location             = <!-- Should be left blank if same as country of origin above.-->\n| cinematography       = \n| editor               = \n| camera               = [[Single-camera]]\n| runtime              = \n| company              = The Unicorn\n| distributor          = [[TVN (South Korean TV channel)|tvN]]\n| network              = tvN\n| picture_format       = [[1080i]] ([[HDTV]])\n| audio_format         = [[Dolby Digital]] \n| first_run            = <!-- The nation in which the series first aired. Should be omitted if the same country as country of origin above. -->\n| first_aired          = {{start date|2018|1|24}}\n| last_aired           = {{end date|2018|3|15}}\n| preceded_by          = <!-- Should not b