ards-has-been-revealed-2017/|archive-date=November 4, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.funandseriousgamefestival.com/awards/|title=Titanium Awards 2017|publisher=Fun & Serious Game Festival|date=December 11, 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180322191455/http://en.funandseriousgamefestival.com/awards|archivedate=March 22, 2018|url-status=dead|accessdate=November 8, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Game Design\n| {{Won}}\n\n|-\n| rowspan=\"32\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2018\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\"| New York Game Awards\n| Big Apple Award for Best Game of the Year\n| {{Nom}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.axs.com/complete-list-of-winners-of-the-new-york-game-awards-2018-127527|title=Complete list of winners of the New York Game Awards 2018|last=Whitney|first=Kayla|date=January 25, 2018|publisher=[[AXS (company)|AXS]]|accessdate=January 27, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401132006/https://www.axs.com/complete-list-of-winners-of-the-new-york-game-awards-2018-127527|archive-date=April 1, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| Central Park Children's Zoo Award for Best Kids Game\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Tin Pan Alley Award for Best Music in a Game\n| {{Nom}}\n\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"4\"| [[21st Annual D.I.C.E. Awards]]\n| Game of the Year\n| {{Nom}}\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/game-of-the-year-nominees-announced-for-dice-award/1100-6456107/|title=Game Of The Year Nominees Announced for DICE Awards|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|date=January 14, 2018|website=GameSpot|accessdate=January 17, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180117131244/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/game-of-the-year-nominees-announced-for-dice-award/1100-6456107/|archive-date=January 17, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/legend-of-zelda-breath-of-the-wild-wins-game-of-th/1100-6456956/|title=Legend Of Zelda: Breath Of The Wild Wins Game Of The Year At DICE Awards|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|date=February 22, 2018|website=GameSpot|accessdate=February 23, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180223161253/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/legend-of-zelda-breath-of-the-wild-wins-game-of-th/1100-6456956/|archive-date=February 23, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| Adventure Game of the Year\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| Outstanding Achievement in Game Design\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| Outstanding Achievement in Sound Design\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"6\"| [[NAVGTR]] Awards\n| Control Design, 3D\n| {{Won}}\n| rowspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://navgtr.org/archives/3351/ |title=Nominee List for 2017 |publisher=[[National Academy of Video Game Trade Reviewers]] |date=February 9, 2018 |accessdate=February 15, 2018 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20180215172210/http://navgtr.org/archives/3351/ |archive-date=February 15, 2018 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=\"Horizon wins 7; Mario GOTY\"/>\n|-\n| Control Precision\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| Game Design, Franchise\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Game of the Year\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Game, Franchise Family\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Song, Original or Adapted (\"Jump Up, Super Star!\")\n| {{Won}}\n\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"4\"| Italian Video Game Awards\n| People's Choice\n| {{Nom}}\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://italianvideogameawards.com/awards |title=Italian Video Game Nominees and Winners 2018 |publisher=Italian Video Game Awards |date=March 14, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180321193010/https://italianvideogameawards.com/awards |archive-date=March 21, 2018 |url-status=dead |access-date=May 31, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| Game of the Year\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| Best Game Design\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Best Character (Cappy)\n| {{Nom}}\n\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"5\"| [[SXSW Gaming Awards]]\n| Excellence in SFX\n| {{Won}}\n| rowspan=\