 Of The Year Award |website=GameSpot |accessdate=March 22, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327162143/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/legend-of-zelda-breath-of-the-wild-wins-another-ga/1100-6457600/ |archive-date=March 27, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n| Game of the Year\n| {{Nom}}\n\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"1\"| Game Audio Network Guild Awards\n| Best Original Song (\"Jump Up, Super Star!\")\n| {{Nom}}\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.audiogang.org/2018-awards/ |title=2018 Awards |publisher=Game Audio Network Guild |accessdate=April 14, 2018 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20180414040621/http://www.audiogang.org/2018-awards/ |archive-date=April 14, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"1\"| [[2018 Kids' Choice Awards]]\n| Favorite Video Game\n| {{Nom}}\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nickpress.com/press-releases/2018/02/26/nickelodeon-announces-2018-kids-choice-awards-nominations |title=NICKELODEON ANNOUNCES 2018 KIDS\u2019 CHOICE AWARDS NOMINATIONS |website=[[Nick.com]] |publisher=[[Viacom (2005\u2013present)|Viacom]] |date=February 26, 2018 |accessdate=March 3, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612135947/http://www.nickpress.com/press-releases/2018/02/26/nickelodeon-announces-2018-kids-choice-awards-nominations |archive-date=June 12, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Drysdale |first=Jennifer |date=March 24, 2018 |url=http://www.etonline.com/2018-kids-choice-awards-the-complete-winners-list-99000 |title=2018 Kids' Choice Awards: The Complete Winners List |publisher=[[Entertainment Tonight]] |accessdate=March 25, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180325052000/http://www.etonline.com/2018-kids-choice-awards-the-complete-winners-list-99000 |archive-date=March 25, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\"| [[14th British Academy Games Awards]]