18-avengers-infinity-war-black-panther-and-riverdale-among-top-nominees |title=Teen Choice Awards 2018: Avengers: Infinity War, Black Panther and Riverdale Among Top Nominees |publisher=[[E!]] |accessdate=June 25, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613220922/https://www.eonline.com/news/943773/teen-choice-awards-2018-avengers-infinity-war-black-panther-and-riverdale-among-top-nominees |archive-date=June 13, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2018/08/teen-choice-awards-winners-list-riverdale-avengers-infinity-war-black-panther-marvel-disney-cw-pixar-fox-1202444357/ |title=Teen Choice Awards: \u2018Riverdale\u2019, \u2018Infinity War\u2019, \u2018Black Panther\u2019 Among Top Honorees \u2013 Full Winners List |last=Ramos |first=Dino-Ray |date=August 12, 2018 |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |accessdate=August 13, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180813061149/https://deadline.com/2018/08/teen-choice-awards-winners-list-riverdale-avengers-infinity-war-black-panther-marvel-disney-cw-pixar-fox-1202444357/ |archive-date=August 13, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"1\"| [[BBC Radio 1|BBC Radio 1's Teen Awards]]\n| Best Game\n| {{Nom}}\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/latestnews/2018/radio-1s-teen-awards |title=Little Mix, 5 Seconds Of Summer, Sigrid and Jonas Blue lead the performances for BBC Radio 1's Teen Awards 2018 |publisher=[[BBC]] |date=September 10, 2018 |accessdate=August 7, 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Notes==\n{{Notelist}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em|refs=\n\n<ref name=\"Gamescom\">{{cite news|title=Super Mario Odyssey sweeps Best Of Gamescom awards|url=http://metro.co.uk/2017/08/24/super-mario-odyssey-sweeps-best-of-gamescom-awards-6876988/|access-date=August 26, 2017|work=Metro|date=August 24, 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827042740/http://metro.co.uk/2017/08/24/