ice|Will Price}}\n|[[Maureen O'Hara]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Tripoli (1950 film)|url=http://www.afi.com/members/catalog/AbbrView.aspx?s=&Movie=26540|website=AFI Catalog of Feature Films|publisher=AFI|accessdate=February 17, 2015}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|''[[Three Husbands]]''\n|Dan McCabe\n|{{sort|Reis|Irving Reis}}\n|[[Eve Arden]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Three Husbands|url=http://www.afi.com/members/catalog/AbbrView.aspx?s=&Movie=26525|website=AFI Catalog of Feature Films|publisher=AFI|accessdate=February 17, 2015}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|scope=\"row\"  rowspan=3|1951\n|''[[Fourteen Hours]]''\n|Deputy Police Chief Moskar\n|[[Henry Hathaway]]\n|[[Richard Basehart]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Fourteen Hours|url=http://www.afi.com/members/catalog/AbbrView.aspx?s=&Movie=50110|website=AFI Catalog of Feature Films.|publisher=AFI|accessdate=February 17, 2015}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|''[[Slaughter Trail]]''\n|Capt. Dempster\n|{{sort|Allen|[[Irving Allen]]}}\n|[[Gig Young]], [[Virginia Grey]]\n|[[Howard Da Silva#Blacklisting|Note]]<ref name=146Humphries/>\n|\n|-\n|''[[M (1951 film)|M]]''\n|Inspector Carney\n|[[Joseph Losey]]\n|[[David Wayne]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=M (1951 film)|url=http://www.afi.com/members/catalog/AbbrView.aspx?s=&Movie=50192|website=AFI Catalog of Feature Films|publisher=AFI|accessdate=February 17, 2015}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|scope=\"row\" |1962\n|''[[David and Lisa]]''\n|Dr. Alan Swinford\n|{{sort|Perry|[[Frank Perry]]}}\n|[[Keir Dullea]], [[Janet Margolin]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=David and Lisa|url=http://www.afi.com/members/catalog/AbbrView.aspx?s=&Movie=23336|website=AFI Catalog of Feature Films|publisher=AFI|accessdate=February 17, 2015}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 |1964\n|{{sort|Outrage|''[[The Outrage (1964 film)|The Outrage]]''}}\n|Prospector\n|{{sort|Ritt|[[Martin Ritt]]}}\n|[[Paul Newman]], [[Laurence Harvey]], [[Claire Bloom]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=The Outrage|url=http://www.afi.com/members/catalog/AbbrView.aspx?s=&Movie=23312|website=AFI Catalog of Feature 